---
import background from "../assets/background.svg";
---

<section id="precios">
  <div
    class="relative isolate bg-[url('../src/assets/background.svg')fixed] dark:bg-slate-950 px-2 py-0 sm:py-24 lg:px-8"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute inset-x-0 -top-3 -z-10 transform-gpu overflow-hidden px-36 blur-3xl"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      <div
        class="aspect-[1155/678] w-[72.1875rem] bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#ff80b5] to-[#9089fc] opacity-30"
        style="clip-path: polygon(74.1% 44.1%, 100% 61.6%, 97.5% 26.9%, 85.5% 0.1%, 80.7% 2%, 72.5% 32.5%, 60.2% 62.4%, 52.4% 68.1%, 47.5% 58.3%, 45.2% 34.5%, 27.5% 76.7%, 0.1% 64.9%, 17.9% 100%, 27.6% 76.8%, 76.1% 97.7%, 74.1% 44.1%)"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-indigo-600">Precios</h2>
      <p
        class="mt-2 text-balance text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl dark:text-white"
      >
        Elige el plan correcto para ti.
      </p>
    </div>
    <p
      class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-pretty text-center text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 sm:text-xl/8 dark:text-white"
    >
      Elige un plan asequible que esté lleno de las mejores características para
      involucrar a tu audiencia, crear lealtad de clientes y aumentar las
      ventas.
    </p>
    <div
      class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-lg grid-cols-1 items-center gap-y-6 sm:mt-20 sm:gap-y-0 lg:max-w-4xl lg:grid-cols-2"
    >
      <div
        class="rounded-3xl rounded-t-3xl bg-white/60 p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-900/10 sm:mx-8 sm:rounded-b-none sm:p-10 lg:mx-0 lg:rounded-bl-3xl lg:rounded-tr-none"
      >
        <h3 id="tier-hobby" class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-indigo-600">
          Pymes/Personales
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-x-2">
          <span class="text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900"
            >$150</span
          >
          <span class="text-base text-gray-500">/Un pago</span>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-base/7 text-gray-600 dark:text-white">
          El plan perfecto si estas comenzando con tu proyecto.
        </p>
        <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-sm/6 text-gray-600 sm:mt-10">
          <li class="flex gap-x-3 dark:text-white">
            <svg
              class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              data-slot="icon"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Landing pages
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3 dark:text-white">
            <svg
              class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              data-slot="icon"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            4 secciones
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3 dark:text-white">
            <svg
              class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              data-slot="icon"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            5GB de almacenamiento
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3 dark:text-white">
            <svg
              class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              data-slot="icon"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            24/7 soporte
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a
          href="#contacto"
          aria-describedby="tier-hobby"
          class="mt-8 block rounded-md px-3.5 py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-600 ring-1 ring-inset ring-indigo-200 hover:ring-indigo-300 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600 sm:mt-10"
          >Empieza hoy</a
        >
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative rounded-3xl bg-gray-900 p-8 shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-gray-900/10 sm:p-10"
      >
        <h3
          id="tier-enterprise"
          class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-indigo-400"
        >
          Empresa/Pymes 2
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-x-2">
          <span class="text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white"
            >$250</span
          >
          <span class="text-base text-gray-400">/Un pago</span>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-base/7 text-gray-300">
          El plan perfecto si ya tienes un proyecto en marcha.
        </p>
        <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-sm/6 text-gray-300 sm:mt-10">
          <li class="flex gap-x-3">
            <svg
              class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-400"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              data-slot="icon"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Pagina Web
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3">
            <svg
              class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-400"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              data-slot="icon"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            10GB de almacenamiento
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3">
            <svg
              class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-400"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              data-slot="icon"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            4 paginas/secciones
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3">
            <svg
              class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-400"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              data-slot="icon"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Correo empresarial
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3">
            <svg
              class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-400"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              data-slot="icon"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            24/7 soporte
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3">
            <svg
              class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-400"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              data-slot="icon"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Integracion a redes sociales
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a
          href="#contacto"
          aria-describedby="tier-enterprise"
          class="mt-8 block rounded-md bg-indigo-500 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-400 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-500 sm:mt-10"
          >Empieza hoy</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <p
      class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-pretty text-center text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 sm:text-xl/8 dark:text-white"
    >
      Consulte por planes de actualizacion y mantencion mensual.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #background {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: -1;
    filter: blur(100px);
  }
</style>
